{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779182281226,"sessionID":"ses_1c079733dfferixSTRfU3JRAe8","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_01_VpHFTKVq6QW1hkelJ3K22953","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/html/frontend"},"output":"<path>/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/html/frontend</path>\n<type>directory</type>\n<entries>\nA-01-landing.html\n\n(1 entries)\n</entries>","metadata":{"preview":"A-01-landing.html","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/design/html/frontend","time":{"start":1779182280782,"end":1779182281216}},"id":"prt_e3f871acb001LC16j4dEM5Ge7i","sessionID":"ses_1c079733dfferixSTRfU3JRAe8","messageID":"msg_e3f86f4b70013K1303ez4a663n"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779182283072,"sessionID":"ses_1c079733dfferixSTRfU3JRAe8","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_02_lP39qGpYCFzmoJb99zz35423","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_A.md"},"output":"<path>/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_A.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # DESIGN_SYSTEM A — Dark Vibrant (Linear-inspired)\n2: \n3: **Archetype:** Dark Vibrant / Glass Morphism\n4: **Reference Company:** Linear\n5: **Generated:** 2026-05-19\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## Design Philosophy\n10: \n11: **Core Inspiration:** Linear's dark, focused interface — minimal chrome, content-first, with vibrant accent colors that guide attention without overwhelming.\n12: \n13: **The Four Pillars:**\n14: - Search & Discovery = Zillow (card patterns, filter hierarchy) + Linear (keyboard-first, fast)\n15: - Property Browsing = Airbnb (photo-first cards, immersive imagery) + Linear (dark mode, reduced glare)\n16: - Dashboard & Admin = Linear (clean, one action per page, neon accent on active states)\n17: - Trust & Credibility = Stripe (generous whitespace, confident typography, no decoration)\n18: \n19: ---\n20: \n21: ## Color System\n22: \n23: ### Background Layer\n24: | Token | Value | Usage |\n25: |-------|-------|-------|\n26: | bg-root | `#0B0F1A` | Page background, body |\n27: | bg-surface | `rgba(255,255,255,0.04)` | Card backgrounds (glass, backdrop-blur) |\n28: | bg-surface-hover | `rgba(255,255,255,0.06)` | Card hover state |\n29: | bg-elevated | `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)` | Modals, dropdowns, elevated surfaces |\n30: | bg-sidebar | `#080B14` | Sidebar background |\n31: \n32: ### Primary / Accent\n33: | Token | Value | Usage |\n34: |-------|-------|-------|\n35: | primary | `#4A90D9` | Base primary (blue) |\n36: | primary-glow | `#4A90D9 → #7C3AED` | Gradient used on CTAs, hero elements |\n37: | primary-hover | `#5BA0E9` | Button hover, link hover |\n38: | primary-muted | `rgba(74,144,217,0.15)` | Selected state backgrounds |\n39: \n40: ### Semantic Colors\n41: | Token | Value | Usage |\n42: |-------|-------|-------|\n43: | success | `#4ADE80` | Active status, success badges |\n44: | success-glow | `0 0 12px rgba(74,222,128,0.4)` | Glow on success badges |\n45: | warning | `#FBBF24` | Pending, warning states |\n46: | warning-glow | `0 0 12px rgba(251,191,36,0.4)` | Glow on warning badges |\n47: | error | `#F87171` | Error, suspended states |\n48: | error-glow | `0 0 12px rgba(248,113,113,0.4)` | Glow on error badges |\n49: \n50: ### Text\n51: | Token | Value | Usage |\n52: |-------|-------|-------|\n53: | text-primary | `#F1F5F9` | Headings, body text |\n54: | text-secondary | `#94A3B8` | Labels, secondary info |\n55: | text-muted | `#64748B` | Captions, metadata |\n56: | text-inverse | `#0B0F1A` | Text on light/white elements |\n57: \n58: ### Borders\n59: | Token | Value | Usage |\n60: |-------|-------|-------|\n61: | border-default | `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)` | Card borders, dividers |\n62: | border-focus | `rgba(74,144,217,0.5)` | Focus rings, active states |\n63: | border-glow | `rgba(74,144,217,0.2)` | Glow border on elevated cards |\n64: \n65: ---\n66: \n67: ## Typography\n68: \n69: | Level | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |\n70: |-------|------|--------|-------------|-------|\n71: | H1 | 48px | 700 | 1.1 | Hero headings only |\n72: | H2 | 36px | 700 | 1.2 | Page titles |\n73: | H3 | 24px | 600 | 1.3 | Section headings |\n74: | H4 | 20px | 600 | 1.4 | Card titles |\n75: | Body | 16px | 400 | 1.6 | Main content |\n76: | Small | 14px | 500 | 1.5 | Labels, metadata |\n77: | Caption | 12px | 400 | 1.4 | Fine print, timestamps |\n78: \n79: **Font Family:** Inter, system-ui, sans-serif\n80: **Letter Spacing:** -0.02em (headings), 0 (body)\n81: \n82: ---\n83: \n84: ## Spacing System\n85: \n86: | Token | Value | Usage |\n87: |-------|-------|-------|\n88: | base | 4px | Grid foundation |\n89: | xs | 4px | Tight inline gaps |\n90: | sm | 8px | Icon-to-label gaps |\n91: | md | 16px | Between elements |\n92: | lg | 24px | Card padding |\n93: | xl | 32px | Section spacing |\n94: | 2xl | 48px | Major section gaps |\n95: | 3xl | 64px | Hero padding |\n96: \n97: ---\n98: \n99: ## Component Specifications\n100: \n101: ### Cards\n102: - Background: `rgba(255,255,255,0.04)` + `backdrop-filter: blur(12px)`\n103: - Border: 1px `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)`\n104: - Border radius: 12px\n105: - Shadow (hover): `0 0 20px rgba(74,144,217,0.15)`\n106: - Padding: 24px\n107: \n108: ### Buttons\n109: - **Primary:** Gradient `#4A90D9 → #7C3AED`, height 48px, radius 12px, glow on hover\n110: - **Secondary:** `rgba(255,255,255,0.06)` bg, 1px border, height 48px, radius 12px\n111: - **Ghost:** Transparent, text-primary, height 40px, radius 8px\n112: \n113: ### Inputs\n114: - Height: 48px, radius: 10px\n115: - Background: `rgba(255,255,255,0.04)`\n116: - Border: 1px `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)`\n117: - Focus: border `rgba(74,144,217,0.5)` + glow ring\n118: \n119: ### Status Badges\n120: - Expression: **Neon glow** — colored text + matching box-shadow glow\n121: - `Active/New`: `#4ADE80` + glow\n122: - `Pending/Warning`: `#FBBF24` + glow\n123: - `Suspended/Error`: `#F87171` + glow\n124: - Radius: 9999px (pill), padding: 2px 10px, font-size: 12px\n125: \n126: ### Sidebar\n127: - Background: `#080B14`\n128: - Width: 240px\n129: - Active item: gradient left border (3px) + `rgba(74,144,217,0.1)` background\n130: - Icons: 20px, text-secondary when inactive, text-primary when active\n131: \n132: ### Shadows\n133: - Card default: `0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3)`\n134: - Card hover: `0 0 20px rgba(74,144,217,0.15)`\n135: - Modal: `0 0 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5)`\n136: - Button CTA: `0 0 24px rgba(74,144,217,0.3)` on hover\n137: \n138: ### Corner Radius Map\n139: - Buttons: 12px\n140: - Cards: 12px\n141: - Inputs: 10px\n142: - Modals: 16px\n143: - Badges: 9999px (pill)\n144: - Avatars: 9999px (circle)\n145: \n146: ---\n147: \n148: ## Interaction States\n149: \n150: | State | Visual |\n151: |-------|--------|\n152: | Hover (card) | bg-surface → bg-surface-hover + glow shadow |\n153: | Focus (input) | border-focus + 0 0 0 3px rgba(74,144,217,0.15) ring |\n154: | Active (button) | Scale 0.98 |\n155: | Disabled | Opacity 0.4, cursor not-allowed |\n156: | Loading | Skeleton shimmer: rgba(255,255,255,0.03) → rgba(255,255,255,0.06) |\n157: \n158: ---\n159: \n160: ## Key Design Rules\n161: 1. Dark background reduces eye strain — use vibrant accents sparingly\n162: 2. Glass morphism cards create depth without heavy borders\n163: 3. Gradient CTAs provide clear visual hierarchy for primary actions\n164: 4. Neon glow badges make status immediately scannable\n165: 5. Generous whitespace between sections (32-64px)\n166: 6. One primary action per view (gradient button)\n167: 7. Keyboard-first interactions where possible\n\n(End of file - total 167 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# DESIGN_SYSTEM A — Dark Vibrant (Linear-inspired)\n\n**Archetype:** Dark Vibrant / Glass Morphism\n**Reference Company:** Linear\n**Generated:** 2026-05-19\n\n---\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\n**Core Inspiration:** Linear's dark, focused interface — minimal chrome, content-first, with vibrant accent colors that guide attention without overwhelming.\n\n**The Four Pillars:**\n- Search & Discovery = Zillow (card patterns, filter hierarchy) + Linear (keyboard-first, fast)\n- Property Browsing = Airbnb (photo-first cards, immersive imagery) + Linear (dark mode, reduced glare)\n- Dashboard & Admin = Linear (clean, one action per page, neon accent on active states)\n- Trust & Credibility = Stripe (generous whitespace, confident typography, no decoration)\n\n---\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_A.md","time":{"start":1779182282758,"end":1779182283070}},"id":"prt_e3f87220a001aAGba8ESm3UKTC","sessionID":"ses_1c079733dfferixSTRfU3JRAe8","messageID":"msg_e3f86f4b70013K1303ez4a663n"}}
