{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1779182321135,"sessionID":"ses_1c079733dfferixSTRfU3JRAe8","part":{"id":"prt_e3f87bdee001Pu0bv2VqiXAIwj","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"d4ea9f1592de42b675d3d68be3e89449ee2a9063","messageID":"msg_e3f875966001eyrwndCzDWyn6X","sessionID":"ses_1c079733dfferixSTRfU3JRAe8","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":33841,"input":5248,"output":120,"reasoning":569,"cache":{"write":0,"read":27904}},"cost":0.011933848}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1779182322699,"sessionID":"ses_1c079733dfferixSTRfU3JRAe8","part":{"id":"prt_e3f87c409001XriaamosqEMZBg","messageID":"msg_e3f87be3000170qRB75ao01Qug","sessionID":"ses_1c079733dfferixSTRfU3JRAe8","snapshot":"fdc6ec23461ae7d04e3d474b32f6bf0084068580","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779182354757,"sessionID":"ses_1c079733dfferixSTRfU3JRAe8","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"skill","callID":"call_00_BCAuxuDy0UzHgJ8JfaHu2523","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"name":"generate-html"},"output":"<skill_content name=\"generate-html\">\n# Skill: generate-html\n\n# Generate HTML\n\n> **Router skill**: Delegates to `generate-html-gemini` (primary, A1) or `prompts-to-html` (fallback, A2) based on GEMINI_API_KEY availability.\n\nThis skill is referenced by the design blueprint for Steps 3e-3g (full HTML generation after variation selection).\n\n---\n\n## Prerequisites\n\n1. **Design Prompts file** at `.claude-project/design/{PROJECT}_DesignPrompts.md` (from Step 3b)\n2. **DESIGN_SYSTEM.md** at `.claude-project/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md` (from Step 3a)\n3. **DESIGN_STATUS.md** with `approved: true` and `selected_variation` (from Step 3d)\n\n---\n\n## Path Selection\n\n| Condition | Path | Skill |\n|-----------|------|-------|\n| `GEMINI_API_KEY` is set | Primary (A1) | `generate-html-gemini/SKILL.md` |\n| `GEMINI_API_KEY` is not set | Fallback (A2) | `prompts-to-html/SKILL.md` |\n\n---\n\n## Workflow\n\n1. Check `GEMINI_API_KEY` environment variable\n2. Read `DESIGN_STATUS.md` to determine selected variation\n3. Delegate to appropriate generation skill\n4. Validate output meets all MANDATORY requirements (device frames, navigation, etc.)\n\n---\n\n## Device Frame Wrapper (MANDATORY)\n\nAll generated HTML pages must render inside an appropriate device frame based on the target platform.\n\n### Platform Detection\n\nDetermine frame type from PRD platform field or page user_type:\n\n| Platform Keywords | Frame Type | Dimensions |\n|-------------------|-----------|------------|\n| mobile, ios, android, webview, react-native | Mobile Phone Frame | 375x812px |\n| tablet, ipad | Tablet Frame | 768x1024px |\n| desktop, web, dashboard, admin | Desktop (no frame) | max-width: 1440px centered |\n\nMixed projects (e.g., consumer=mobile + admin=desktop): detect per page based on user_type.\n\n### Mobile Phone Frame HTML Template\n\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"...\">\n<head>\n  <!-- CDN links -->\n  <style>\n    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }\n    html, body { height: 100%; background: #111; /* #e5e5e5 for light themes */ }\n    .phone-frame {\n      width: 375px; height: 812px; margin: 24px auto;\n      background: VAR_BG_COLOR; color: VAR_TEXT_COLOR;\n      border-radius: 40px; border: 3px solid #2a2a3a;\n      overflow: hidden; position: relative;\n      box-shadow: 0 0 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.4), 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);\n    }\n    .phone-screen { height: 100%; overflow-y: auto; padding-bottom: 80px; scrollbar-width: none; }\n    .phone-screen::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }\n    .bottom-bar { position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100; }\n    .phone-frame::before { /* Notch */\n      content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);\n      width: 150px; height: 28px; background: VAR_BG_COLOR;\n      border-radius: 0 0 18px 18px; z-index: 200;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"phone-frame\">\n    <div class=\"phone-screen\">\n      <!-- Status Bar -->\n      <div style=\"height:48px;padding:14px 20px 0;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;\">9:41</span>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:5px;align-items:center;\">\n          <iconify-icon icon=\"mdi:signal-cellular-3\" width=\"14\"></iconify-icon>\n          <iconify-icon icon=\"mdi:wifi\" width=\"14\"></iconify-icon>\n          <iconify-icon icon=\"mdi:battery\" width=\"18\"></iconify-icon>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- PAGE CONTENT HERE -->\n\n      <div style=\"height:80px;\"></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"bottom-bar\"><!-- Bottom navigation --></div>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n### Rules\n- WARNING: `position:fixed` PROHIBITED inside phone frame -- use `position:absolute`\n- WARNING: Notch `::before` background MUST match variation's main background color\n- WARNING: Status bar text: light color for dark themes, dark color for light themes\n- WARNING: Outer body background: `#111` for dark themes, `#e5e5e5` for light themes\n- The `var-nav-bar` (in-page variation navigation) is the ONLY exception allowed to use `position:fixed`\n\n### Desktop Frame\nNo device frame needed. Use: `body { max-width: 1440px; margin: 0 auto; }`\n\n### In-Page Variation Navigation (MANDATORY)\n\nEvery generated HTML file must include a floating nav bar for switching between pages in the same variation:\n- Position: fixed, top-right corner\n- Semi-transparent dark background with backdrop-blur\n- Links to all pages in the same variation (01, 02, 03, 04)\n- Current page highlighted\n- X button links to showcase-ALL.html\n\n---\n\n## Related Skills\n\n- `.claude/skills/design/generate-html-gemini/SKILL.md` -- Primary path (Gemini API)\n- `.claude/skills/design/prompts-to-html/SKILL.md` -- Fallback path (Claude)\n- `.claude/skills/design/prd-to-design-guide/SKILL.md` -- Step 3a: PRD to design guide\n- `.claude/skills/design/design-guide-to-prompts/SKILL.md` -- Step 3b: Design guide to prompts\n\nBase directory for this skill: file:///Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude/skills/design/generate-html\nRelative paths in this skill (e.g., scripts/, reference/) are relative to this base directory.\nNote: file list is sampled.\n\n<skill_files>\n\n</skill_files>\n</skill_content>","metadata":{"name":"generate-html","dir":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude/skills/design/generate-html","truncated":false},"title":"Loaded skill: generate-html","time":{"start":1779182354417,"end":1779182354755}},"id":"prt_e3f883d49001CeGA23q7KhOy3y","sessionID":"ses_1c079733dfferixSTRfU3JRAe8","messageID":"msg_e3f87be3000170qRB75ao01Qug"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779182357330,"sessionID":"ses_1c079733dfferixSTRfU3JRAe8","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_01_iRYb7jMAsDCOnWFvuwzW5880","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/html/frontend/A-01-landing.html","limit":100},"output":"<path>/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/html/frontend/A-01-landing.html</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: <!DOCTYPE html>\n2: <html lang=\"en\">\n3: <head>\n4: <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n5: <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n6: <title>NestFind — Find Your Next Home</title>\n7: <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n8: <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n9: <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@iconify/iconify@2.2.1/dist/iconify.min.js\"></script>\n10: <style>\n11: *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}\n12: body{font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;background:#0B0F1A;color:#F1F5F9;line-height:1.6}\n13: .root{max-width:1440px;margin:0 auto}\n14: .navbar{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:16px 48px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)}\n15: .nav-logo{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4A90D9,#7C3AED);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent}\n16: .nav-links{display:flex;gap:32px;align-items:center}\n17: .nav-links a{color:#94A3B8;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;transition:color 0.2s}\n18: .nav-links a:hover{color:#F1F5F9}\n19: .btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;border:none;transition:all 0.2s;font-family:inherit;text-decoration:none}\n20: .btn-primary{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4A90D9,#7C3AED);color:#fff;height:48px;padding:0 24px;border-radius:12px;font-size:14px}\n21: .btn-primary:hover{box-shadow:0 0 24px rgba(74,144,217,0.3);transform:translateY(-1px)}\n22: .btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:#F1F5F9;height:40px;padding:0 16px;border-radius:8px;font-size:14px}\n23: .btn-ghost:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)}\n24: .hero{padding:80px 48px 64px;text-align:center}\n25: .hero h1{font-size:48px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:16px;letter-spacing:-0.02em}\n26: .hero h1 span{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4A90D9,#7C3AED);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent}\n27: .hero p{color:#94A3B8;font-size:18px;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 32px}\n28: .search-bar{display:flex;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;gap:0}\n29: .search-bar input{flex:1;height:56px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-right:none;border-radius:12px 0 0 12px;padding:0 20px;color:#F1F5F9;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;outline:none}\n30: .search-bar input:focus{border-color:rgba(74,144,217,0.5);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(74,144,217,0.1)}\n31: .search-bar input::placeholder{color:#64748B}\n32: .search-bar .btn-primary{border-radius:0 12px 12px 0;height:56px;padding:0 32px;font-size:16px}\n33: .chip-row{display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;margin-top:24px;flex-wrap:wrap}\n34: .chip{padding:8px 16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:9999px;font-size:13px;color:#94A3B8;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s}\n35: .chip:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);color:#F1F5F9}\n36: .section{padding:64px 48px}\n37: .section-label{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;color:#4A90D9;margin-bottom:8px}\n38: .section h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:16px;letter-spacing:-0.02em}\n39: .section p.sub{color:#94A3B8;font-size:16px;max-width:560px;margin-bottom:48px}\n40: .steps{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px}\n41: .step-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:12px;padding:32px 24px;text-align:center;transition:all 0.3s}\n42: .step-card:hover{box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(74,144,217,0.15);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)}\n43: .step-num{width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:12px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4A90D9,#7C3AED);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;margin:0 auto 16px}\n44: .step-card h4{font-size:18px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px}\n45: .step-card p{color:#94A3B8;font-size:14px}\n46: .property-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px}\n47: .prop-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;transition:all 0.3s}\n48: .prop-card:hover{box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(74,144,217,0.15);transform:translateY(-2px)}\n49: .prop-img{width:100%;height:200px;object-fit:cover;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(74,144,217,0.3),rgba(124,58,237,0.3))}\n50: .prop-body{padding:20px}\n51: .prop-price{font-size:22px;font-weight:700}\n52: .prop-addr{color:#94A3B8;font-size:14px;margin:4px 0 8px}\n53: .prop-meta{display:flex;gap:16px;font-size:13px;color:#64748B}\n54: .badge{display:inline-block;padding:2px 10px;border-radius:9999px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px}\n55: .badge-new{color:#4ADE80;box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(74,222,128,0.3)}\n56: .features{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:24px}\n57: .feat-card{text-align:center;padding:24px}\n58: .feat-icon{width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(74,144,217,0.1);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 12px;color:#4A90D9}\n59: .feat-card h4{font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:6px}\n60: .feat-card p{color:#94A3B8;font-size:13px}\n61: footer{border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);padding:48px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between}\n62: .footer-col h5{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin-bottom:16px;color:#64748B}\n63: .footer-col a{display:block;color:#94A3B8;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:8px;transition:color 0.2s}\n64: .footer-col a:hover{color:#F1F5F9}\n65: .var-nav-bar{position:fixed;top:12px;right:12px;display:flex;gap:6px;background:rgba(8,11,20,0.9);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);padding:6px 10px;border-radius:10px;z-index:9999;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);font-size:11px;flex-wrap:wrap;max-width:95vw}\n66: .var-nav-bar a{color:#64748B;text-decoration:none;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;padding:3px 7px;border-radius:5px;transition:all 0.2s;white-space:nowrap}\n67: .var-nav-bar a.active{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4A90D9,#7C3AED);color:#fff}\n68: .var-nav-bar a:hover:not(.active){color:#F1F5F9;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)}\n69: .var-nav-bar .sep{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);font-size:10px}\n70: </style>\n71: </head>\n72: <body>\n73: <nav class=\"var-nav-bar\">\n74: <a href=\"A-01-landing.html\" class=\"active\">Landing</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n75: <a href=\"A-02-admin-dashboard.html\">Dashboard</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n76: <a href=\"A-03-detail.html\">Detail</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n77: <a href=\"A-04-search.html\">Search</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n78: <a href=\"A-05-login.html\">Login</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n79: <a href=\"A-06-register.html\">Register</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n80: <a href=\"A-07-forgot-password.html\">Reset</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n81: <a href=\"A-08-favorites.html\">Favorites</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n82: <a href=\"A-09-profile.html\">Profile</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n83: <a href=\"A-10-admin-properties.html\">Properties</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n84: <a href=\"A-11-admin-property-form.html\">PropForm</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n85: <a href=\"A-12-admin-inquiries.html\"