{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779182967422,"sessionID":"ses_1c079733dfferixSTRfU3JRAe8","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_00_otLETZrIZy5C0Kn2Oamd3480","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Generate auth HTML pages","subagent_type":"general","prompt":"\nGenerate 4 HTML files for NestFind auth pages using Design System A (Dark Vibrant / Linear). Write them to `.claude-project/nestfind/design/html/frontend/`.\n\n## DESIGN TOKENS (Design System A)\n- bg-root: #0B0F1A\n- bg-surface: rgba(255,255,255,0.04)\n- bg-surface-hover: rgba(255,255,255,0.06)\n- bg-elevated: rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\n- bg-sidebar: #080B14\n- primary: #4A90D9\n- primary-glow gradient: #4A90D9 → #7C3AED\n- text-primary: #F1F5F9\n- text-secondary: #94A3B8\n- text-muted: #64748B\n- border-default: rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\n- success: #4ADE80 (with glow)\n- warning: #FBBF24 (with glow)\n- error: #F87171 (with glow)\n\n## CSS CLASSES (copy EXACTLY from existing A-01-landing.html)\nEvery page MUST include these exact CSS classes in a `<style>` block:\n```css\n*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}\nbody{font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;background:#0B0F1A;color:#F1F5F9;line-height:1.6}\n.root{max-width:1440px;margin:0 auto}\n.navbar{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:16px 48px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)}\n.nav-logo{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4A90D9,#7C3AED);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent}\n.nav-links{display:flex;gap:32px;align-items:center}\n.nav-links a{color:#94A3B8;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;transition:color 0.2s}\n.nav-links a:hover{color:#F1F5F9}\n.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;border:none;transition:all 0.2s;font-family:inherit;text-decoration:none}\n.btn-primary{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4A90D9,#7C3AED);color:#fff;height:48px;padding:0 24px;border-radius:12px;font-size:14px}\n.btn-primary:hover{box-shadow:0 0 24px rgba(74,144,217,0.3);transform:translateY(-1px)}\n.btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:#F1F5F9;height:40px;padding:0 16px;border-radius:8px;font-size:14px}\n.btn-ghost:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)}\n.btn-secondary{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);color:#F1F5F9;height:48px;padding:0 24px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);font-size:14px}\n.btn-secondary:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1)}\n.btn-danger{background:rgba(248,113,113,0.15);color:#F87171;height:40px;padding:0 16px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(248,113,113,0.2);font-size:13px}\n.btn-danger:hover{background:rgba(248,113,113,0.25)}\n.card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:12px;padding:24px}\n.card:hover{box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(74,144,217,0.15);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)}\ninput[type=\"text\"],input[type=\"email\"],input[type=\"password\"],input[type=\"tel\"],textarea,select{height:48px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:10px;padding:0 16px;color:#F1F5F9;font-size:14px;font-family:inherit;outline:none;width:100%}\ninput:focus,textarea:focus,select:focus{border-color:rgba(74,144,217,0.5);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(74,144,217,0.1)}\ninput::placeholder,textarea::placeholder{color:#64748B}\ntextarea{height:auto;padding:12px 16px;resize:vertical;min-height:100px}\nlabel{display:block;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:#94A3B8;margin-bottom:6px}\n.form-group{margin-bottom:16px}\n.form-link{color:#4A90D9;font-size:13px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500}\n.form-link:hover{color:#5BA0E9}\n.badge{display:inline-block;padding:2px 10px;border-radius:9999px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600}\n.badge-success{color:#4ADE80;box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(74,222,128,0.3)}\n.badge-warning{color:#FBBF24;box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(251,191,36,0.3)}\n.badge-error{color:#F87171;box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(248,113,113,0.3)}\n.var-nav-bar{position:fixed;top:12px;right:12px;display:flex;gap:6px;background:rgba(8,11,20,0.9);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);padding:6px 10px;border-radius:10px;z-index:9999;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);font-size:11px;flex-wrap:wrap;max-width:95vw}\n.var-nav-bar a{color:#64748B;text-decoration:none;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;padding:3px 7px;border-radius:5px;transition:all 0.2s;white-space:nowrap}\n.var-nav-bar a.active{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4A90D9,#7C3AED);color:#fff}\n.var-nav-bar a:hover:not(.active){color:#F1F5F9;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)}\n.var-nav-bar .sep{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);font-size:10px}\n.error-text{color:#F87171;font-size:12px;margin-top:4px}\n.divider{height:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);margin:24px 0}\n```\n\n## GLOBAL TEMPLATE STRUCTURE\nEach file must follow this structure exactly:\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>NestFind — PAGE_TITLE</title>\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@iconify/iconify@2.2.1/dist/iconify.min.js\"></script>\n<style>\n/* ALL CSS CLASSES GO HERE */\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<nav class=\"var-nav-bar\">\n  <!-- ALL page links; current page gets class=\"active\" -->\n</nav>\n<div class=\"root\">\n<nav class=\"navbar\">\n  <div class=\"nav-logo\">NestFind</div>\n  <div class=\"nav-links\">\n    <a href=\"A-06-search.html\">Browse</a>\n    <a href=\"A-01-landing.html\">Home</a>\n  </div>\n</nav>\n<!-- PAGE CONTENT -->\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n## VAR-NAV-BAR (include in EVERY file, update active class for current page)\n```html\n<nav class=\"var-nav-bar\">\n<a href=\"A-01-landing.html\">Landing</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-02-login.html\">Login</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-03-signup.html\">Signup</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-04-forgot-password.html\">Forgot</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-05-reset-password.html\">Reset</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-06-search.html\">Search</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-07-detail.html\">Detail</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-08-favorites.html\">Favs</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-09-inquiries.html\">Inq</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-10-profile.html\">Prof</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-11-admin-login.html\">AdLog</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-12-admin-dashboard.html\">AdDash</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-13-admin-properties.html\">AdProp</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-14-admin-property-form.html\">AdForm</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-15-admin-inquiries.html\">AdInq</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-16-admin-users.html\">AdUsr</a>\n</nav>\n```\n\n## FILES TO CREATE\n\n### 1. A-02-login.html\nPage title: \"Sign In\"\nContent centered vertically and horizontally. Card (max-width 420px) with:\n- \"Welcome back\" heading (h2, 28px)\n- \"Sign in to your account\" subtitle\n- Email input with label\n- Password input with label + \"Forgot password?\" link on the right\n- \"Sign In\" btn-primary full width\n- Divider with \"or\" text\n- \"Don't have an account? Sign up\" link\n- Footer text: \"By signing in you agree to our Terms and Privacy Policy\"\n\n### 2. A-03-signup.html\nPage title: \"Create Account\"\nCard (max-width 420px) with:\n- \"Create your account\" heading\n- \"Join NestFind to save favorites and submit inquiries\" subtitle\n- Full Name input\n- Email input\n- Phone input (optional badge)\n- Password input\n- Confirm Password input\n- \"Create Account\" btn-primary full width\n- Terms checkbox: \"I agree to the Terms of Service and Privacy Policy\"\n- Divider + \"Already have an account? Sign in\" link\n\n### 3. A-04-forgot-password.html\nPage title: \"Forgot Password\"\nCard (max-width 420px) with:\n- \"Reset your password\" heading\n- \"Enter your email and we'll send you a reset link\" subtitle\n- Email input\n- \"Send Reset Link\" btn-primary full width\n- \"Back to Sign In\" link centered\n\n### 4. A-05-reset-password.html\nPage title: \"Reset Password\"\nCard (max-width 420px) with:\n- \"Set new password\" heading\n- \"Choose a strong password for your account\" subtitle\n- New Password input with hint \"At least 8 characters\"\n- Confirm New Password input\n- \"Reset Password\" btn-primary full width\n- Success state: a second view (hidden by default) showing check icon, \"Password reset successful!\" message, and \"Back to Sign In\" link\n\n## IMPORTANT RULES:\n- ALL pages use `body{background:#0B0F1A}` and `color:#F1F5F9}` — DARK THEME\n- Auth pages center content with a flex container on the full viewport: `display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:100vh;padding:24px`\n- No external CSS files — all styles inline in `<style>` block\n- Use iconify icons where appropriate (e.g., `<span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:email-outline\"></span>` for icons)\n- Keep HTML clean, well-indented, and production-quality\n- Each file should be self-contained and look professional\n\nWrite ALL 4 files. Do NOT skip any. Return a summary of which files were written and their content.\n"},"output":"task_id: ses_1c074710cffeJy0ON0Ocgzf7zJ (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nAll 4 files written to `.claude-project/nestfind/design/html/frontend/`:\n\n| File | Size | Content |\n|------|------|---------|\n| `A-02-login.html` | 7.9 KB | \"Welcome back\" — email, password with forgot link, remember me checkbox, Sign In button, divider, sign up link, terms text |\n| `A-03-signup.html` | 8.4 KB | \"Create your account\" — full name, email, phone (optional badge), password, confirm password, terms checkbox, Create Account button, sign in link |\n| `A-04-forgot-password.html` | 7.0 KB | \"Reset your password\" — lock icon, email input, Send Reset Link button, Back to Sign In link |\n| `A-05-reset-password.html` | 8.0 KB | \"Set new password\" — new password with \"At least 8 characters\" hint, confirm password, Reset Password button. Hidden success view with check icon and \"Back to Sign In\" link |\n\nAll pages use the exact CSS classes specified, the correct var-nav-bar (with `active` on self), dark theme (#0B0F1A), centered auth cards (max-width 420px), and the global navbar with Browse/Home links.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_1c079733dfferixSTRfU3JRAe8","sessionId":"ses_1c074710cffeJy0ON0Ocgzf7zJ","model":{"modelID":"deepseek-v4-pro","providerID":"opencode-go"},"truncated":false},"title":"Generate auth HTML pages","time":{"start":1779182571255,"end":1779182967420}},"id":"prt_e3f89f4d70014ZrYq8fTZGf0kD","sessionID":"ses_1c079733dfferixSTRfU3JRAe8","messageID":"msg_e3f896300001aECEP4TqKR6Rl2"}}
