{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779183635536,"sessionID":"ses_1c079733dfferixSTRfU3JRAe8","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_01_4L4QLetLks97bRUMfleJ0509","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Generate renter HTML pages 1","subagent_type":"general","prompt":"\nGenerate 4 HTML files for NestFind renter pages using Design System A (Dark Vibrant / Linear). Write them to `.claude-project/nestfind/design/html/frontend/`.\n\n## DESIGN TOKENS (Design System A)\n- bg-root: #0B0F1A\n- bg-surface: rgba(255,255,255,0.04)\n- bg-surface-hover: rgba(255,255,255,0.06)\n- bg-elevated: rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\n- primary: #4A90D9\n- primary-glow gradient: #4A90D9 → #7C3AED\n- text-primary: #F1F5F9\n- text-secondary: #94A3B8\n- text-muted: #64748B\n- border-default: rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\n- border-focus: rgba(74,144,217,0.5)\n- success: #4ADE80 (with glow: 0 0 8px rgba(74,222,128,0.3))\n- warning: #FBBF24 (with glow)\n- error: #F87171 (with glow)\n\n## FULL CSS (copy this EXACT `<style>` block into every file)\n```css\n*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}\nbody{font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;background:#0B0F1A;color:#F1F5F9;line-height:1.6}\n.root{max-width:1440px;margin:0 auto}\n.navbar{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:16px 48px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)}\n.nav-logo{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4A90D9,#7C3AED);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent}\n.nav-links{display:flex;gap:32px;align-items:center}\n.nav-links a{color:#94A3B8;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;transition:color 0.2s}\n.nav-links a:hover{color:#F1F5F9}\n.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;border:none;transition:all 0.2s;font-family:inherit;text-decoration:none}\n.btn-primary{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4A90D9,#7C3AED);color:#fff;height:48px;padding:0 24px;border-radius:12px;font-size:14px}\n.btn-primary:hover{box-shadow:0 0 24px rgba(74,144,217,0.3);transform:translateY(-1px)}\n.btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:#F1F5F9;height:40px;padding:0 16px;border-radius:8px;font-size:14px}\n.btn-ghost:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)}\n.btn-secondary{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);color:#F1F5F9;height:48px;padding:0 24px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);font-size:14px}\n.btn-secondary:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1)}\n.btn-sm{height:36px;padding:0 14px;border-radius:8px;font-size:13px}\n.btn-icon{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:8px;background:transparent;color:#94A3B8;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;border:none}\n.btn-icon:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);color:#F1F5F9}\n.card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:12px;padding:24px}\n.card-hover{transition:all 0.3s}\n.card-hover:hover{box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(74,144,217,0.15);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);transform:translateY(-2px)}\ninput[type=\"text\"],input[type=\"email\"],input[type=\"password\"],input[type=\"tel\"],input[type=\"number\"],textarea,select{height:48px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:10px;padding:0 16px;color:#F1F5F9;font-size:14px;font-family:inherit;outline:none;width:100%}\ninput:focus,textarea:focus,select:focus{border-color:rgba(74,144,217,0.5);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(74,144,217,0.1)}\ninput::placeholder,textarea::placeholder{color:#64748B}\ntextarea{height:auto;padding:12px 16px;resize:vertical;min-height:100px}\nlabel{display:block;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:#94A3B8;margin-bottom:6px}\n.badge{display:inline-block;padding:2px 10px;border-radius:9999px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600}\n.badge-success{color:#4ADE80;box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(74,222,128,0.3)}\n.badge-warning{color:#FBBF24;box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(251,191,36,0.3)}\n.badge-error{color:#F87171;box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(248,113,113,0.3)}\n.badge-new{color:#4ADE80;box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(74,222,128,0.3)}\n.chip{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:6px 14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:9999px;font-size:13px;color:#94A3B8;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s}\n.chip:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);color:#F1F5F9}\n.chip.active{background:rgba(74,144,217,0.15);border-color:rgba(74,144,217,0.4);color:#4A90D9}\n.prop-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;transition:all 0.3s}\n.prop-card:hover{box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(74,144,217,0.15);transform:translateY(-2px)}\n.prop-img{width:100%;height:200px;object-fit:cover;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(74,144,217,0.3),rgba(124,58,237,0.3))}\n.prop-body{padding:20px}\n.prop-price{font-size:22px;font-weight:700}\n.prop-addr{color:#94A3B8;font-size:14px;margin:4px 0 8px}\n.prop-meta{display:flex;gap:16px;font-size:13px;color:#64748B;flex-wrap:wrap}\n.section{padding:48px}\n.section-header{margin-bottom:32px}\n.section-label{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;color:#4A90D9;margin-bottom:8px}\n.section h2{font-size:32px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;letter-spacing:-0.02em}\ntable{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse}\nth{text-align:left;padding:12px 16px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;color:#64748B;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)}\ntd{padding:14px 16px;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);color:#F1F5F9}\ntr:hover td{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02)}\n.var-nav-bar{position:fixed;top:12px;right:12px;display:flex;gap:6px;background:rgba(8,11,20,0.9);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);padding:6px 10px;border-radius:10px;z-index:9999;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);font-size:11px;flex-wrap:wrap;max-width:95vw}\n.var-nav-bar a{color:#64748B;text-decoration:none;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;padding:3px 7px;border-radius:5px;transition:all 0.2s;white-space:nowrap}\n.var-nav-bar a.active{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4A90D9,#7C3AED);color:#fff}\n.var-nav-bar a:hover:not(.active){color:#F1F5F9;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)}\n.var-nav-bar .sep{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);font-size:10px}\n.fav-btn{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border:none;color:#94A3B8;cursor:pointer;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all 0.2s}\n.fav-btn:hover{background:rgba(248,113,113,0.15);color:#F87171}\n.fav-btn.active{background:rgba(248,113,113,0.2);color:#F87171}\n.gallery-img{width:100%;height:400px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:12px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(74,144,217,0.2),rgba(124,58,237,0.2))}\n.thumb-strip{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:12px}\n.thumb{width:80px;height:60px;border-radius:8px;object-fit:cover;cursor:pointer;border:2px solid transparent;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);transition:all 0.2s}\n.thumb:hover{border-color:rgba(74,144,217,0.3)}\n.thumb.active{border-color:#4A90D9}\n.status-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:8px}\n.status-new{background:#4ADE80;box-shadow:0 0 6px rgba(74,222,128,0.4)}\n.status-read{background:#64748B}\n.status-responded{background:#4A90D9;box-shadow:0 0 6px rgba(74,144,217,0.4)}\n.map-placeholder{width:100%;height:300px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(74,144,217,0.1),rgba(124,58,237,0.1));border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#64748B;font-size:14px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)}\n.page-header{padding:48px 48px 0}\n.empty-state{text-align:center;padding:80px 24px}\n.empty-state .empty-icon{width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:16px;background:rgba(74,144,217,0.08);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 16px;color:#4A90D9}\n.empty-state h3{font-size:20px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px}\n.empty-state p{color:#94A3B8;font-size:14px;max-width:360px;margin:0 auto 24px}\n.amenities-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:12px}\n.amenity-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border-radius:8px;font-size:14px;color:#94A3B8}\n.amenity-item .iconify{color:#4A90D9}\n.modal-overlay{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.7);backdrop-filter:blur(4px);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;z-index:1000}\n.modal{background:#0D1320;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:16px;padding:32px;max-width:480px;width:90%;box-shadow:0 0 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5)}\n.modal h3{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px}\n.modal p{color:#94A3B8;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:24px}\n.stats-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px}\n.stat-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:12px;padding:24px;text-align:center}\n.stat-card h3{font-size:32px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px}\n.stat-card p{color:#94A3B8;font-size:13px}\n.tabs{display:flex;gap:0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);margin-bottom:24px}\n.tab{padding:10px 20px;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:#64748B;cursor:pointer;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;transition:all 0.2s;background:none;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-right:none;font-family:inherit}\n.tab:hover{color:#F1F5F9}\n.tab.active{color:#4A90D9;border-bottom-color:#4A90D9}\n.pagination{display:flex;gap:4px;justify-content:center;margin-top:32px}\n.page-btn{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:#94A3B8;cursor:pointer;background:transparent;border:none;transition:all 0.2s;font-family:inherit}\n.page-btn:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);color:#F1F5F9}\n.page-btn.active{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4A90D9,#7C3AED);color:#fff}\n</style>\n```\n\n## VAR-NAV-BAR TEMPLATE (include in every file, mark current page active):\n```html\n<nav class=\"var-nav-bar\">\n<a href=\"A-01-landing.html\">Landing</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-02-login.html\">Login</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-03-signup.html\">Signup</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-04-forgot-password.html\">Forgot</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-05-reset-password.html\">Reset</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-06-search.html\">Search</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-07-detail.html\">Detail</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-08-favorites.html\">Favs</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-09-inquiries.html\">Inq</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-10-profile.html\">Prof</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-11-admin-login.html\">AdLog</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-12-admin-dashboard.html\">AdDash</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-13-admin-properties.html\">AdProp</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-14-admin-property-form.html\">AdForm</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-15-admin-inquiries.html\">AdInq</a><span class=\"sep\">|</span>\n<a href=\"A-16-admin-users.html\">AdUsr</a>\n</nav>\n```\n\n## PAGES TO CREATE\n\n### 1. A-06-search.html — Property Search (Home)\nFull-width page with:\n- Top filter bar: search input (location), filter dropdowns (Price Range, Bedrooms, Property Type), Sort dropdown\n- Active chips showing current filters (removable)\n- Property count text \"Showing 24 properties\"\n- Grid of property cards (4 columns, 8 cards shown). Each card:\n  - Image placeholder (200px tall, gradient)\n  - Heart/favorite icon button\n  - Badge (New, Featured, etc.)\n  - Price: \"$1,850/mo\"\n  - Address: \"123 Main St, Austin, TX\"\n  - Bed/Bath/SqFt meta row\n- Pagination at bottom (1 2 3 ... 8)\n- Map toggle button in top-right corner\n\n### 2. A-07-detail.html — Property Detail\nFull property detail page with:\n- Photo gallery: large main image (400px), thumbnail strip below (5 thumbs)\n- Property header: price, address, badge\n- Key stats row: Beds | Baths | Sq Ft | Property Type (4 stat cards)\n- Description section with full text\n- Amenities grid (2 columns, 8 amenities with icons)\n- Map placeholder section\n- Contact/Inquiry section: form with Name, Email, Phone, Message + \"Send Inquiry\" button\n- Back to search link at top\n- Favorite toggle\n\n### 3. A-08-favorites.html — Favorites\nPage with:\n- Page header: \"My Favorites\" with count\n- Grid of 6 property cards (matching search card style, with heart icon filled red)\n- Empty state (hidden by default): \"No favorites yet\" with heart icon, \"Start browsing and save properties you love\" message, \"Browse Properties\" button\n- Each card has a \"Remove\" button (btn-secondary sm)\n\n### 4. A-09-inquiries.html — My Inquiries\nPage with:\n- Page header: \"My Inquiries\" with count\n- Table of inquiries:\n  - Property (name + link)\n  - Date Sent\n  - Status badge (New/Read/Responded with status-dot)\n  - Actions (View button)\n- 5 rows of sample inquiry data\n- Empty state (hidden): \"No inquiries yet\"\n\n## FILE STRUCTURE\n```\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>NestFind — PAGE_TITLE</title>\n  <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n  <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@iconify/iconify@2.2.1/dist/iconify.min.js\"></script>\n  <style>\n    /* ALL CSS ABOVE */\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<nav class=\"var-nav-bar\">\n  <!-- current page gets class=\"active\" -->\n</nav>\n<div class=\"root\">\n<nav class=\"navbar\">\n  <div class=\"nav-logo\">NestFind</div>\n  <div class=\"nav-links\">\n    <a href=\"A-06-search.html\">Browse</a>\n    <a href=\"A-08-favorites.html\">Favorites</a>\n    <a href=\"A-09-inquiries.html\">My Inquiries</a>\n    <a href=\"A-10-profile.html\">Profile</a>\n  </div>\n</nav>\n<!-- PAGE CONTENT -->\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n## RULES\n- Dark theme: bg #0B0F1A, text #F1F5F9\n- Desktop layout (no phone frame) — max-width: 1440px\n- All icons use: `<span class=\"iconify\" data-icon=\"mdi:ICON_NAME\"></span>`\n- NO Tailwind CSS — use only the CSS classes defined above\n- EVERY FILE must include the complete CSS block and var-nav-bar\n- Each page must be fully populated with realistic sample data\n- Use icon names from Material Design Icons (mdi:) prefix\n\nWrite ALL 4 files. Return a summary of each file created.\n"},"output":"task_id: ses_1c071c2a9ffeNyTcC62LkGIPH6 (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nAll 4 files created in `.claude-project/nestfind/design/html/frontend/`:\n\n| File | Size | Summary |\n|------|------|---------|\n| **A-06-search.html** | 22K | Property search with filter bar (location, price, beds, type, sort), active filter chips, \"Showing 24 properties\" count, 8 property cards in 4-column grid (with badges, prices, addresses, bed/bath/sqft meta), pagination (1-8), map toggle button |\n| **A-07-detail.html** | 17K | Full property detail with gallery (main image + 5 thumbs), price/address/badge header, 4 stat cards (beds, baths, sqft, type), description, 2-column amenities grid (8 items), map placeholder, sticky inquiry form with name/email/phone/message fields, back-to-search link, active heart favorite |\n| **A-08-favorites.html** | 20K | \"My Favorites (6)\" header, 6 property cards in 3-column grid (all hearts filled red/active), each with View Details + Remove buttons, commented-out empty state with heart icon and Browse Properties CTA |\n| **A